	<h2>SocialHappen Privacy Policy</h2>
	<p>SocialHappen Co.,Ltd. ("SocialHappen") operates several websites including Socialhappen.com, apps.facebook.com/socialhappen, facebook.com/socialhappen, and including other applications operating under SocialHappen brand. It is SocialHappen’s policy to respect your privacy regarding any information we may collect while operating our websites.</p>
