		</li>
		<li>
			<h5>Cookies</h5>
			A cookie is a string of information that a website stores on a visitor’s computer, and that the visitor’s browser provides to the website each time the visitor returns. SocialHappen uses cookies to help SocialHappen identify and track visitors, their usage of SocialHappen website, and their website access preferences. SocialHappen visitors who do not wish to have cookies placed on their computers should set their browsers to refuse cookies before using SocialHappen’s websites, with the drawback that certain features of SocialHappen’s websites may not function properly without the aid of cookies.
		</li>
